      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<p>
	  The meritorious gift of a maṇḍapa and cistern by
	  <persName key="pers:Ayama">Ayama</persName> of the
	  Vatsa gotra, prime minister of the king Mahākṣatrapa Svāmi
	  <persName key="pers:Nahapāna">Nahapāna</persName>,
	  made for merit, in the year 46.
	</p>
